(Xiao Ran,
come to the rendezvous point.)

30
00:02:15,989 --> 00:02:17,748
(Warriors.)

31
00:02:18,109 --> 00:02:20,549
(You are entrusted
with a greater mission.)

32
00:02:20,868 --> 00:02:24,349
(You will travel to where
the past and the future connect.)

33
00:02:26,188 --> 00:02:27,708
(The treasure hidden there)

34
00:02:27,708 --> 00:02:31,829
(can restore order
to this chaotic time.)

35
00:02:42,549 --> 00:02:44,069
Look at the graphics

36
00:02:44,708 --> 00:02:45,949
and this beautiful view.

37
00:02:46,109 --> 00:02:48,148
As expected of the game I created.

38
00:02:48,708 --> 00:02:49,509
It's extraordinary.

39
00:02:50,509 --> 00:02:51,989
(After you cross the Gate of Void,)

40
00:02:51,989 --> 00:02:53,308
(your mission will begin.)

41
00:02:53,468 --> 00:02:54,989
(Those who embark on this mission)

42
00:02:55,509 --> 00:02:57,349
(will have a dangerous path
ahead of you.)

43
00:02:57,349 --> 00:02:58,708
It's show time for me.

44
00:03:11,468 --> 00:03:12,708
Who's shaking me

45
00:03:12,708 --> 00:03:13,748
at this time?

46
00:03:13,748 --> 00:03:15,588
System error, please log in again.

47
00:03:15,588 --> 00:03:16,109
Lingling!

48
00:03:16,428 --> 00:03:17,188
Lingling!

49
00:03:19,789 --> 00:03:20,669
Ms. Guo.

50
00:03:21,188 --> 00:03:22,069
Why are you here?

51
00:03:22,628 --> 00:03:24,148
You scared me.

52
00:03:24,148 --> 00:03:25,989
Are you ill again?

53
00:03:26,410 --> 00:03:27,789
Let's go to the hospital right now.

54
00:03:27,789 --> 00:03:28,748
Come.

55
00:03:28,748 --> 00:03:29,789
Mom, I'm fine.

56
00:03:29,789 --> 00:03:30,829
I was working just now.

57
00:03:31,069 --> 00:03:32,509
You call sleeping working?

58
00:03:32,750 --> 00:03:34,109
I want to do this kind of work too.

59
00:03:34,109 --> 00:03:36,069
(The hidden boss
is the embodiment of wisdom.)

60
00:03:36,349 --> 00:03:38,829
(Please choose whether or not
you will accept this test.)

61
00:03:38,829 --> 00:03:40,109
The rest of you should attack
the hidden monster.

62
00:03:40,109 --> 00:03:40,989
I'll clear the stage.

63
00:03:41,829 --> 00:03:43,389
Then we can speed up

64
00:03:43,390 --> 00:03:45,060
so that it won't affect
the market launch.

65
00:03:48,428 --> 00:03:49,588
Well. I really have to work.

66
00:03:49,588 --> 00:03:51,308
Just put it here. I'll eat it later.

67
00:03:51,868 --> 00:03:54,428
Is your work more important
or my love for you?

68
00:04:01,200 --> 00:04:02,148
You are more important.

69
00:04:04,610 --> 00:04:05,908
You don't have to worry about me.

70
00:04:05,908 --> 00:04:07,308
I'll eat.

71
00:04:07,468 --> 00:04:08,428
Finish it.

72
00:04:08,460 --> 00:04:08,980
(Metaverse of Love)

73
00:04:13,229 --> 00:04:14,669
Who's the insolent intruder?

74
00:04:26,748 --> 00:04:29,748
(The combat power of the stage boss
is indeed formidable.)

75
00:04:32,549 --> 00:04:33,828
This is strange.

76
00:04:34,229 --> 00:04:35,308
I didn't feel so ill at ease

77
00:04:35,669 --> 00:04:38,308
when he fought in the past.

78
00:04:49,589 --> 00:04:50,149
Darling!

79
00:04:52,149 --> 00:04:52,709
Let's go.

80
00:04:55,828 --> 00:04:56,909
What's going on?

81
00:04:56,909 --> 00:04:57,820
Why is he running away?

82
00:05:03,029 --> 00:05:03,789
General.

83
00:05:04,149 --> 00:05:04,748
Darling.

84
00:05:05,029 --> 00:05:07,589
I don't think I can make it.

85
00:05:09,388 --> 00:05:09,909
Darling.

86
00:05:12,268 --> 00:05:13,149
Darling!

87
00:05:16,229 --> 00:05:17,149
You scoundrel!

88
00:05:18,909 --> 00:05:20,669
You killed my family.

89
00:05:22,029 --> 00:05:23,589
I will kill you

90
00:05:24,308 --> 00:05:26,669
in my next life to avenge my family!

91
00:05:38,060 --> 00:05:39,700
(The game cannot be logged in.)

92
00:05:40,740 --> 00:05:41,828
There's a bug with the game.

93
00:05:47,068 --> 00:05:48,109
What's going on?

94
00:05:49,109 --> 00:05:50,109
Boss. This is bad.

95
00:05:50,109 --> 00:05:51,480
Something is wrong with the system.

96
00:05:51,630 --> 00:05:52,909
Wait for me. I'll be there soon.

97
00:05:52,909 --> 00:05:53,549
Okay.

98
00:06:05,589 --> 00:06:07,029
Boss.

99
00:06:08,589 --> 00:06:09,469
Boss!

100
00:06:10,589 --> 00:06:11,789
Ask for help!

101
00:06:11,989 --> 00:06:12,508
Be careful.

102
00:06:12,508 --> 00:06:14,029
Boss. Call the ambulance.

103
00:06:14,029 --> 00:06:15,748
Hello. Is this the emergency center?

104
00:06:15,748 --> 00:06:17,000
Someone here who has passed out.

105
00:06:17,508 --> 00:06:18,589
Lan Yao Studio.

106
00:06:19,068 --> 00:06:19,709
Yes.

107
00:06:20,109 --> 00:06:20,828
Okay.

108
00:06:24,229 --> 00:06:24,709
Here.

109
00:06:25,308 --> 00:06:25,748
Be careful.

110
00:06:42,068 --> 00:06:42,828
Brother.

111
00:06:42,828 --> 00:06:44,268
The board of directors
want to see you.

112
00:06:44,268 --> 00:06:44,989
Everyone pays

113
00:06:44,989 --> 00:06:46,669
close attention to this beta test.

114
00:06:46,948 --> 00:06:48,149
With such a huge mistake,

115
00:06:48,789 --> 00:06:51,530
Uncle Chen and the others
will probably be quite mean later.

116
00:06:52,828 --> 00:06:54,789
I just received a call
from the hospital

117
00:06:54,789 --> 00:06:56,420
saying that Dad
is throwing a tantrum again.

118
00:06:56,709 --> 00:06:58,109
I'll accompany him at the hospital.

119
00:06:58,109 --> 00:06:59,188
Go to the meeting first.

120
00:06:59,188 --> 00:06:59,868
Remember.

121
00:06:59,868 --> 00:07:00,989
Don't act recklessly.

122
00:07:00,989 --> 00:07:02,068
Play it by ear.

123
00:07:02,068 --> 00:07:03,068
Don't worry.

124
00:07:03,068 --> 00:07:04,029
I can handle it.

125
00:07:09,989 --> 00:07:10,709
I'm told

126
00:07:10,709 --> 00:07:12,508
that Shanhai Group is investing

127
00:07:12,508 --> 00:07:14,229
in a game called "Metaverse of Love".

128
00:07:14,229 --> 00:07:15,469
Both the NPCs

129
00:07:15,469 --> 00:07:16,789
and the graphics of the game

130
00:07:16,789 --> 00:07:18,549
are immersive and enjoyable, right?

131
00:07:18,549 --> 00:07:19,109
Of course.

132
00:07:19,388 --> 00:07:20,268
Shanhai Group

133
00:07:20,268 --> 00:07:21,868
has always aimed for perfection.

134
00:07:22,750 --> 00:07:23,748
The center of attention

135
00:07:23,748 --> 00:07:25,428
is the gaming platform for this game.

136
00:07:25,428 --> 00:07:27,628
Unlike traditional gaming platforms,

137
00:07:27,628 --> 00:07:29,428
with the most advanced technology,

138
00:07:29,628 --> 00:07:31,508
the players just need
to close their eyes

139
00:07:31,508 --> 00:07:32,549
and enjoy

140
00:07:32,549 --> 00:07:35,868
this groundbreaking game
immersively in their brain.

141
00:07:36,268 --> 00:07:36,989
Shanhai Group

142
00:07:36,989 --> 00:07:38,349
will hold a conference

143
00:07:38,349 --> 00:07:41,030
with the master creator of the game,
Lan Yao Studio, in a week's time.

144
00:07:41,229 --> 00:07:43,388
I'm told that the female designer
of this game,

145
00:07:43,388 --> 00:07:44,149
Goddess Lanyao,

146
00:07:44,149 --> 00:07:46,469
is a genius
who studied overseas, right?

147
00:07:46,469 --> 00:07:47,828
I really look forward

148
00:07:47,828 --> 00:07:49,828
to witnessing Goddess Lanyao's

149
00:07:49,828 --> 00:07:50,628
creativity.

150
00:07:51,400 --> 00:07:53,349
You have a shareholder's meeting
in half an hour,

151
00:07:53,349 --> 00:07:54,469
a video conference at eight tonight

152
00:07:54,469 --> 00:07:56,589
with the manufacturer
of the gaming glasses.

153
00:07:56,828 --> 00:07:57,669
Next,

154
00:07:58,388 --> 00:07:59,349
take a look at this.

155
00:07:59,349 --> 00:08:00,930
Our Public Sentiment Department
is analyzing

156
00:08:01,109 --> 00:08:03,229
the feedback of the netizens
toward this game.

157
00:08:03,229 --> 00:08:04,748
The Public Relations Department
is handling the media.

158
00:08:05,160 --> 00:08:05,909
What about Lanyao?

159
00:08:06,068 --> 00:08:07,068
I can't reach her.

160
00:08:08,029 --> 00:08:09,709
I can't reach her on her phone.

161
00:08:09,868 --> 00:08:12,068
Make sure I see Lanyao after the meeting.

162
00:08:12,068 --> 00:08:12,909
Okay, Boss.

163
00:08:13,940 --> 00:08:18,820
