164
00:08:40,109 --> 00:08:41,388
Where am I?

165
00:08:42,668 --> 00:08:44,388
Why don't I recognize this place?

166
00:08:50,628 --> 00:08:51,508
Am I

167
00:08:52,548 --> 00:08:54,388
dead?

168
00:09:15,989 --> 00:09:17,069
My fellow elder.

169
00:09:17,268 --> 00:09:18,548
Can you lend me

170
00:09:18,548 --> 00:09:19,748
your mount?

171
00:09:21,949 --> 00:09:23,548
After I find my wife,

172
00:09:23,548 --> 00:09:26,069
I'll reward you handsomely.

173
00:09:26,069 --> 00:09:27,709
No need to be so courteous.

174
00:09:28,388 --> 00:09:32,028
But this mount is passed down
from my ancestors.

175
00:09:32,548 --> 00:09:34,268
I can't simply give it to someone else.

176
00:09:34,268 --> 00:09:34,989
I understand.

177
00:09:36,829 --> 00:09:37,748
How about this?

178
00:09:38,589 --> 00:09:41,349
I'm willing to exchange it
with my treasure.

179
00:09:46,548 --> 00:09:47,788
Come forth, my hammers!

180
00:09:52,548 --> 00:09:54,028
Where's my hammer?

181
00:09:56,388 --> 00:09:57,949
It must be due to the wrong posture.

182
00:10:00,469 --> 00:10:01,429
Come forth, my hammers!

183
00:10:05,189 --> 00:10:06,109
Come forth, my hammers!

184
00:10:07,268 --> 00:10:08,190
Come forth, my hammers!

185
00:10:09,069 --> 00:10:10,069
Come forth, my hammers!

186
00:10:14,868 --> 00:10:15,668
Old man.

187
00:10:16,868 --> 00:10:20,788
I must have lost my power
after the great fight.

188
00:10:21,429 --> 00:10:23,028
That's why I can't summon my hammers.

189
00:10:24,109 --> 00:10:26,589
Can you give me a few more days?

190
00:10:26,868 --> 00:10:28,229
I'll exchange them for your mount.

191
00:10:29,589 --> 00:10:30,908
No need to trouble yourself.

192
00:10:31,949 --> 00:10:32,908
I'm touched

193
00:10:32,908 --> 00:10:35,349
by the love between you and your wife.

194
00:10:35,868 --> 00:10:37,189
Now, I've decided

195
00:10:37,548 --> 00:10:39,709
to give this to you as a gift.

196
00:10:42,508 --> 00:10:43,628
You are a hero.

197
00:10:43,989 --> 00:10:46,548
I will repay you for your kindness.

198
00:10:47,028 --> 00:10:47,668
Have a seat.

199
00:10:47,668 --> 00:10:48,268
Okay.

200
00:10:48,650 --> 00:10:49,989
I asked you to wait for me
after the test.

201
00:10:49,989 --> 00:10:51,949
Where are you running off to?

202
00:10:52,868 --> 00:10:53,668
I...

203
00:10:53,908 --> 00:10:55,788
I'm heading back to my ward.

204
00:10:55,788 --> 00:10:57,668
Do you remember which ward it is?

205
00:10:59,508 --> 00:11:01,109
Psychiatric ward no. 6.

206
00:11:01,109 --> 00:11:02,229
At least you know.

207
00:11:05,069 --> 00:11:05,989
Old man.

208
00:11:05,989 --> 00:11:07,028
My mount.

209
00:11:07,668 --> 00:11:08,868
Enough. Stop it.

210
00:11:16,069 --> 00:11:17,230
Hello, my fellow shareholders.

211
00:11:18,908 --> 00:11:20,949
Metaverse of Love

212
00:11:20,949 --> 00:11:23,628
is indeed forward-looking
and innovative.

213
00:11:23,628 --> 00:11:26,148
However, it requires a lot of funds.

214
00:11:26,628 --> 00:11:27,469
Mr. Li.

215
00:11:27,640 --> 00:11:29,388
You must have invested
a lot in it, right?

216
00:11:30,109 --> 00:11:31,989
Now that there's an issue with it,

217
00:11:31,989 --> 00:11:33,589
what should we do?

218
00:11:33,868 --> 00:11:36,268
We should stop investing in it
to cut our losses.

219
00:11:37,189 --> 00:11:37,788
Right?

220
00:11:38,589 --> 00:11:39,829
The issue during the beta test

221
00:11:40,148 --> 00:11:41,309
is just a minor

222
00:11:41,309 --> 00:11:42,469
technical problem.

223
00:11:42,829 --> 00:11:46,229
Please believe that Lanyao and I will
resolve it as soon as possible.

224
00:11:47,189 --> 00:11:49,430
Lanyao? What does she call herself again?

225
00:11:50,069 --> 00:11:51,388
The Goddess of Game.

226
00:11:52,589 --> 00:11:54,268
Young people now

227
00:11:54,268 --> 00:11:56,069
are so confident

228
00:11:56,069 --> 00:11:57,949
despite not being capable.

229
00:11:58,748 --> 00:12:01,028
Mr. Chen, are you doubting my choice?

230
00:12:01,028 --> 00:12:02,668
No.

231
00:12:06,989 --> 00:12:08,148
I have the veto power.

232
00:12:08,469 --> 00:12:08,949
You...

233
00:12:13,628 --> 00:12:14,388
Mr. Chen.

234
00:12:14,788 --> 00:12:15,949
Mr. Chen.

235
00:12:15,949 --> 00:12:16,989
Are you okay, Mr. Chen?

236
00:12:18,028 --> 00:12:19,309
Mr. Chen.

237
00:12:19,309 --> 00:12:21,868
You need to trust Mr. Xiao.

238
00:12:21,868 --> 00:12:23,748
He won't make a wrong judgment.

239
00:12:24,309 --> 00:12:26,148
We need Mr. Xiao

240
00:12:26,469 --> 00:12:28,748
to help us with our retirement funds.

241
00:12:29,508 --> 00:12:31,229
If we can't launch the game

242
00:12:31,229 --> 00:12:33,309
within the designated time,

243
00:12:34,429 --> 00:12:37,829
I'll take full responsibility for it
to compensate you for your losses.

244
00:12:38,148 --> 00:12:41,189
Since you are so confident,

245
00:12:41,589 --> 00:12:43,109
let me add another condition.

246
00:12:44,229 --> 00:12:45,908
If the project fails,

247
00:12:46,429 --> 00:12:47,148
shouldn't you

248
00:12:47,148 --> 00:12:49,868
quit as the CEO?

249
00:12:56,469 --> 00:12:56,989
Okay.

250
00:12:58,069 --> 00:12:58,908
Deal.

251
00:13:01,949 --> 00:13:03,028
Why are you here?

252
00:13:04,420 --> 00:13:05,940
(Men's Toilet)

253
00:13:05,989 --> 00:13:07,189
Is this the men's toilet?

254
00:13:07,189 --> 00:13:07,949
It is.

255
00:13:15,309 --> 00:13:15,868
Why...

256
00:13:16,628 --> 00:13:17,589
Why is it gone?

257
00:13:27,748 --> 00:13:28,908
Who are you?

258
00:13:53,148 --> 00:13:55,069
I've turned into a woman.

259
00:13:55,950 --> 00:13:56,349
Hurry up.

260
00:13:56,349 --> 00:13:57,388
She's right inside.

261
00:13:58,429 --> 00:13:59,189
Here.

262
00:13:59,829 --> 00:14:02,028
It's really you.
I told you not to run around, right?

263
00:14:03,548 --> 00:14:04,189
Yes, that's her.

264
00:14:04,189 --> 00:14:04,829
That's her.

265
00:14:04,829 --> 00:14:06,148
It's improper for men and women
to touch each other.

266
00:14:06,148 --> 00:14:06,788
That's her.

267
00:14:06,788 --> 00:14:08,949
Why didn't you think it was improper
when you knocked me out?

268
00:14:08,949 --> 00:14:10,109
You can't do this.

269
00:14:12,628 --> 00:14:13,628
Stop running around.

270
00:14:13,628 --> 00:14:14,748
Rest up.

271
00:14:15,309 --> 00:14:17,148
I'm a warrior.

272
00:14:17,148 --> 00:14:19,628
But I'm caught by two women.

273
00:14:20,069 --> 00:14:21,069
This body

274
00:14:21,069 --> 00:14:22,668
is really useless.

275
00:14:22,949 --> 00:14:24,349
Don't run around again.

276
00:14:26,748 --> 00:14:27,868
You have my words.

277
00:14:33,508 --> 00:14:34,630
Let's report this to our dean

278
00:14:34,949 --> 00:14:36,709
and transfer her
to the psychiatric ward.

279
00:14:37,069 --> 00:14:38,709
She's too much trouble.

280
